      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0355P0_20001025_WH_80'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mrs-diana-organ' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0355P0_20001025_WH_80' title='Link to this speech by Mrs Diana Organ' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mrs-diana-organ" title="Mrs Diana Organ">Mrs. Organ</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            May I just say many thanks to the Minister? I shall pass on her good wishes to the free miners in the Forest of Dean.
          </p>
