      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0355P0_20001025_WH_81'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mrs-ray-michie' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0355P0_20001025_WH_81' title='Link to this speech by Mrs Ray Michie' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mrs-ray-michie" title="Mrs Ray Michie">Mrs. Ray Michie</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            We have come to the end of a very interesting debate, and I thank both participants.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S6CV0355P0_20001025_WH_82' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="italic">Question put and agreed to.</span>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S6CV0355P0_20001025_WH_83' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="italic">Adjourned accordingly at three minutes to Two o'clock.</span>
      </p>
